When Mrs. Effat arrives, she finds herself facing a huge challenge keeping up with the kids.

programme.title: Awar Qalb

programme.desc: Twenty years after the end of the Lebanese Civil War, Teresa still cannot get over the death of her brother by a Syrian bomb. She is busy preparing for a visit from her only daughter's fiance, along with his family, who are to stay in their house for the night. When she opens the door for them, she discovers that they are Syrians, which causes her to start sabotaging the marriage.

programme.title: Hold Your Position
programme.desc: Ayman is a casting agent who lives a very liberal life. Hazem is a responsible man who lives a routine life with his wife and kids. As their different personalities pit them against each other, their lives intertwine in the wake of a strange experiment.

programme.title: Mutluluk Zamani

programme.title: Ali Baba
programme.desc: Ali is an opportunistic person who only cares about his own interests, even at the expense of others. When he discovers that he has a daughter in her twenties, he experiences a number of comedic paradoxes.

programme.title: Scales

programme.title: Detained

programme.title: Al-Khawaga's Dilemma

programme.title: The Remaining Time
programme.desc: A short film that follows a woman who finds herself locked in a room with a stranger, as they try to survive the night in the aftermath of an alien invasion.

programme.title: The Most Dangerous Man
